âŒ **Schema tightly coupled with Java classes** â€“ Hard to manage updates across multiple services.

âŒ **Hierarchical and inter-referenced schemas** â€“ Complex dependencies between BookingPackage, Deal, Borrower, etc.

âŒ **Scalability issues** â€“ Schema changes cause disruptions across services.



