### **Slide 5: Schema Versioning Strategy**

ğŸ“Œ **Versioning Approach:**

- **Minor Versions (1.1 â†’ 1.2)** â€“ Backward-compatible changes (new fields).

- **Major Versions (1.x â†’ 2.0)** â€“ Breaking changes (removed fields, structural changes).

- **Patch Versions (1.1.0 â†’ 1.1.1)** â€“ Bug fixes, typos, comments.



ğŸ“Œ **Schema Storage Format:**

| Schema Name | Version | Format | Stored As |

|-------------|---------|--------|-----------|

| LoanIQ | 1.0.0 | JSON | `{ "BookingPackage": { "Deal": { ... } }}` |

| LoanIQ | 1.1.0 | JSON | `{ "BookingPackage": { "Deal": { "NewField": "string" } }}` |

| LoanIQ | 2.0.0 | JSON | `{ "NewStructure": { ... } }` |



