### **Slide 7: Benefits of the New System**

âœ… **No Breaking Changes** â€“ Old services keep using previous schema versions.

âœ… **Dynamic Schema Fetching** â€“ No hardcoded Java DTOs, fully dynamic.

âœ… **Scalable & Flexible** â€“ Schema evolves without disrupting services.

âœ… **GraphQL Integration** â€“ Fetch only required schema parts.

âœ… **Backward Compatibility Ensured** â€“ Automatic validation before updating schemas.



